'''Michael Murnane''' is a concept artist/sculptor, and the author of the short story "[[Wat Tambor and the Quest for the Sacred Eye of the Albino Cyclops]]" in ''[[Star Wars: Visionaries]]''. His work can be seen in ''[[The Art of Star Wars Episode II: Attack of the Clones]]'' and ''[[The Art of Revenge of the Sith]]''.

